  <brief_title>Rerouting Seton Versus LIFT for Complex Anal Fistula</brief_title>
  <official_title>External Anal Sphincter-Sparing Seton After Rerouting Versus Ligation of Intersphincteric Fistula Tract (LIFT) In Treatment Of Complex Anal Fistula: A Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
